      <p><a href="https://metacpan.org/dist/Rex">MetaCPAN</a> / <a href="http://twitter.com/RexOps">Twitter</a> / <a href="https://stackshare.io/rex">StackShare</a> / <a href="http://serverfault.com/questions/tagged/rex">Server Fault</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-.Ã´.-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.disclaimer.de/disclaimer.htm" target="_blank">Disclaimer</a></p>
   </div>

   </body>

</html>
